descript.abstract: Cell site locations within the City of San Diego and other incorporated cities within the County of San Diego. Other incorporated cities include Oceanside, Carlsbad, San Marcos, Escondido, Poway, Santee, El Cajon, Lemon Grove, National City, Imperial Beach, Encinitas, Solana Beach, and Del Mar.
descript.supplinf: This layer was derived from a layer that DPLU originally received from the FCC. The cell towers in the unincorporated portion of the county were removed leaving only those towers in the City of San Diego and other incorporated cities. The PLACES_CELL_SITES_CN contains all cell sites in the unincorporated portion of the County of San Diego and is now being maintained through KIVA. This layer was created to retain those cell sites in the incorporated portion of the County of San Diego. (City of San Diego, Oceanside, Carlsbad, San Marcos, Escondido, Poway, Santee, El Cajon, Lemon Grove, National City, Imperial Beach, Encinitas, Solana Beach, and Del Mar.)
